description:
DOCTORS WORLDWIDE ARE SPEAKING OUT!

Over 500 Doctors speak out against this Scam. And for all the people leaving stupid comments such as “the virus is real” - we know that. There is a virus. People have had it and died from it. But people die of the flu, tuberculosis, pneumonia and many other viruses and we don’t shut the world economy down, make people wear stupid, senseless masks, social distance and attack and turn against their neighbors. It’s disgusting to see how some people are behaving and treating each other. If you’re one of them, you need to check yourself and ask if losing your humanity was worth it. And store managers, corporations, businesses who have adopted these tyrannical policies: we are going to remember what you did. We are going to file lawsuits and we will not shop in your stores again. I personally will change my entire life around not to patronize these places again. I will order my medications online. I will not attend churches who were silent or even blocked me when I tried to share some truth. I will buy produce locally from farmers markets only. I will do everything in my power NOT to support these businesses who trained their employees to go after us like we were diseased criminals for not wearing a damn mask. @cvspharmacy @pavilions @sprouts @followyourheart @petco @pressedjuicery @ladreamcenter @homedepot calvarywestlake oasisla @ralphsgrocery @starbucks 
Watch. Share. Learn.
